required_parameters.name: location

optional_parameters.description:

- `single_family`
- `condos`
- `townhome`
- `multi_family`

- `farm`

optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties without HOA fee only.

optional_parameters.description: The number of results. Maximum 200, default 50

optional_parameters.description: `true` for New construction only. Leave it blank for any
